query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('binomial',
'cross-validation',
'delphi',
'drush',
'i18n-l10n',
'migration',
'model-selection',
'multivariate-analysis',
'pdf',
'prediction',
'random-forest',
'search',
'svm')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('drupal',
'pt',
'stats')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Citizen Patrol',
'Curious',
'Custodian',
'Necromancer',
'Nice Question',
'Promoter',
'Revival') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
